movie_title: Star Wars: Episode I - The Phantom Menace
title: Hmmmm. What can I say.....
review: The plot is awesome, but I don't know about those special effects.  I mean, knowing what we know about it all being fake, how can you not percive everything as a bluscreen with computer images in front of it.  It really detracts from the movie I think, but then again.... That's just my opinion.
